This paper deals with improving the quality of tractography results computed from DW-MRI data using a PDE framework. The paper involves image processing, machine learning, and numerical analysis techniques, which are commonly associated with the computer vision (cs.CV), machine learning (cs.LG), numerical analysis (cs.NA), information theory (cs.IT), and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories of arXiv CS. Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
